Privacy Statement
Relaxby App

Responsible:
Nico Dötsch, Berlinstraße 109, 55411 Bingen, Germany
E-Mail: davdodevelopment@gmail.com


App functions:
This app can play sounds and record the own voice without connecting to the internet.

Personal data tracking:
This app wont track any personal user data. 
This app wont work with any personal user date.

App permissions:
This app needs microphone and storage permission for a correct functionality.

Saving of app data:
This app only saves from the user selected data of specific recordings. 
This saved data can be deleted by the user. 
This saved data will remain saved if the app is closed.
This saved data wont be uploaded and wont be shared in any way.

Geospatial data:
This app wont access at any point geospatial data of the user.
